Abigail. It says, how weird is hiring right now? Are you swamped with applications? Are some of

00:21:20.300 --> 00:21:24.859
them fake people? Are you changing anything about how you do it? Hiring is one of those

00:21:24.859 --> 00:21:29.739
questions where some people do a lot of hiring and some people don't. What experience have you

00:21:29.739 --> 00:21:37.339
